<ab facs="#facs_165_r1l17"><expan>Jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_165_r1l18">nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Alſo tun wır eẅch <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu wıſſen daʒ vns von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_165_r1l19"><expan>merklıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / dıe vns nıht <expan>füklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein ʒu offembarn </ab>
