</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan>, als ir uns aber
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der Gomprechtin
                                <expan>jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also tun wir ewch
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> zu wissen, daz uns von
                                <expan>merklich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die uns niht
                            <expan>füklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein zu offembarn, niht
                                <expan>füklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist
                            <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Gomprechtin<ex>n</ex></expan>, geleyt bey uns zu
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> masse bey uns zeren zu
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>, das in gut von uns
                                <expan>aufczuneme<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab>
</div>
